 Distributed Authoring Group<body>
  Distributed Authoring Group  
    Distributed Authoring Group 



   Goal: to make distributed authoring as pervasive as browsing is today. 

 How? 

  By specifying:  Preliminary modifications to existing specifications (e.g., HTTP)  Usage conventions (e.g., URL name space)    Ensure that distributed web content authoring tools are broadly interoperable     
 
   

